Bandar Raya Stock Advances on Asset-Sale Proposal, Cash Dividend

-- B y   C h a n   T i e n   H i n
-- 
2011-09-20T01:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/bandar-raya-stock-advances-on-asset-sale-proposal-cash-dividend.html
Bandar Raya Developments Bhd. (BRD)  rose
to its highest level in almost two weeks after saying it will
sell its office and malls for 430 million ringgit and give part
of the proceeds to shareholders via a cash dividend.  The stock gained 2.5 percent to 2.44 ringgit at 9:04 a.m.
local time in Kuala Lumpur trading, set for its highest close
since Sept. 8.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chan Tien Hin at 
 thchan@bloomberg.net  